messageBody:
Hi friends,
I am Junayed Chowdhury from Bangladesh. You will please to know that
in our country there are lots of young people who are eager to learn
Java and it's technology even though Java is not so new to us. I
realized that it is necessary to create a Java programmers group in
Bangladesh because it can play an important role to keep communicates
easily with all the programmers like this group. I honorable invited
junit members and moderator to keep in touch with us (Bangladesh Java
Users Group "BDJUG"). This is really grateful to us. Our BDJUG web
site address is www.groups.yahoo.com/group/BDJUG or
www.bdjug.cjb.net.

Best regards,
Junayed Chowdhury
Moderator BDJUG
